Just returned from 3 night stay at the Iroquois
This is our 3rd stay at this property over a 4 year period
Great location
great staff
Walking distance to 5th Avenue
Madison Avenue
Grand Central Station
Times Square
Rockefellar Center
Rooms size wise are what you expect in NYC
Rooms are nicely appointed
great Flat Screen TV and bathroom
Very nice fitness room on 3rd floor
Will definitely stay again
